{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b85af1a24","title":"对慧荣臻关于山东回民支队整编问题的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fef4eee738","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":4,"articleId":"3b85af1a24"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"07e2e7cb6c","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3b85af1a24","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中国人民解放军代总参谋长楚荣臻关于各种工程部队和屯垦部队的调拨与建设计划的报告上写的批语。"},{"id":"482c1062c8","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3b85af1a24","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1952年1月2日曼荣臻给毛泽东并朱德、周思来和林彪的报告中提出的关于各种工程部队和屯星部队的调拨与建设的计划。该计划将全国工程部队增至21个师，计21万人，另以19个师，计19万人，组成屯垦部队。"}],"contents":[{"id":"477a8dc200","type":"title","text":"以四十方军队转为工程军和屯垦军是完全可能的”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3b85af1a24"},{"id":"07e2e7cb6c","type":"paragraph","text":"这个计划很好。按照铁道兵团的经验，以四十万军队转为工程军和屯星军是完全可能的，而且在经济上是很合算而有大利的，国家文立即增加四十万工业工人和使用机器的农业工人。应即刻筹办，并请苏联帮助，中财委订购工程和农业的机器，开办工程学校和农业技术学校。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3b85af1a24"},{"id":"482c1062c8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3b85af1a24"},{"id":"5420af6e19","type":"paragraph","text":"一月四日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3b85af1a24"}],"page":{"id":"5660439b9d","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3b85af1a24","start":230,"end":230}}}},"__N_SSG":true}